-- Day 3: Clean CDC stream

## Day 3 – Real-time Stream Processing (ksqlDB)

- Created cleaned streams from Debezium CDC topics
- Used ksqlDB to flatten CDC envelopes
- Demonstrated real-time data flow from MySQL → Kafka → ksqlDB
- Applied offset management for historical replay
## Day 4 – Real-time Analytics & Alerts

- Built business-ready Kafka streams using ksqlDB
- Created real-time aggregations (orders per plant)
- Implemented alert streams for high-volume orders
- Prepared data for analytics sinks (S3 / Snowflake)



